summary: An ordinance repealing Ordinance No. 8359 entitled: " An ordinance relating to and providing for the improvement of Woodland Park Avenue, in the City of Seattle, form Ewing Street to North 41st Street, by grading the same, all in accordance with Resolution No. 141; of the city council of the City of Seattle; and providing payment therefor by the mode of "Payment in Bonds" for local improvements, providing for the payment thereof, and declaring an emergency", approved March 14, 1899, and Ordinance No. 5693 of said city, approved December 6, 1899."
